column5: so, who do you guys think is gunna win the daytona 500 race this year? i havent been following nascar lately. only seen a couple races last season. so hopefully someone can fill me in on whats changed, any different drivers? hopefully kenseth is still in there  .    JP
ha.....hahahahaha!!! your dreamin' lol! but then again theres always a slight sliver of a chance for gordon to take it
I take J.r (not because im a fan) He has always been strong here and waht a way to start his come back..Vickers will be up there as usual too..
Montoya, all the way! Afterall he's the only guy with a Superlicense in the race, he has to be the best right?
He has another kid on the way,i see that as extra motivation. plus he doesnt do to bad at the 500.  anyone but the shurb. i cant stand looking at him
Ricky Bobby all the way....SHAKE AND BAKE!!!!!!
ohhhh hell ya man!!!!!   montoya (i think) is a good driver too so he's another guy to go for!
I would really like to see Martin pull of the win myself. But if he can't do it then I'll settle for Litte E.
